for your dinner like everyone else.

1032
01:07:11,093 --> 01:07:12,151
RAT 2: Come on, Smudge,
give us a little look.

1033
01:07:12,228 --> 01:07:13,320
SMUDGE: No, no, no!

1034
01:07:13,396 --> 01:07:15,864
SMUDGE: Boss doesn't want her getting
nervous. Spoils the meat, doesn't it?

1035
01:07:18,601 --> 01:07:19,659
