1048
01:07:55,271 --> 01:07:56,295
(GRUNTS)

1049
01:08:55,464 --> 01:08:56,488
Whoa!

1050
01:08:59,802 --> 01:09:00,826
Ha-ha!

1051
01:09:07,176 --> 01:09:08,643
Oh, oh!

1052
01:09:17,319 --> 01:09:18,911
