1068
01:10:34,330 --> 01:10:35,592
Oh, come on.

1069
01:10:36,665 --> 01:10:37,689
Oh!

1070
01:10:42,671 --> 01:10:43,695
Hey, Sire!

1071
01:10:44,773 --> 01:10:46,365
Your Highness!

1072
01:10:46,609 --> 01:10:48,600
