1104
01:12:02,184 --> 01:12:04,948
The Princess is in danger,
and she's down in the dungeon

1105
01:12:05,020 --> 01:12:07,648
and you've gotta... You've gotta help me!

1106
01:12:07,756 --> 01:12:09,121
Somebody?

1107
01:12:21,670 --> 01:12:22,694
Whoa!

1108
01:12:22,805 --> 01:12:24,705
