1137
01:14:59,962 --> 01:15:00,986
Oh!

1138
01:15:01,697 --> 01:15:03,824
Look up there!
Marge, come and have a look at this!

1139
01:15:03,932 --> 01:15:04,956
Oh, my!

1140
01:15:06,702 --> 01:15:07,760
(SNIFFING)

1141
01:15:10,973 --> 01:15:11,997
Mmm!

1142
01:15:16,378 --> 01:15:17,504
Cauliflower?

1143
01:15:17,613 --> 01:15:19,274
Perfect. Perfect, yes, it's about time.

1144
01:15:19,348 --> 01:15:20,610
<i>Basilico.</i>

1145
01:15:21,183 --> 01:15:22,377
Eh, some celery?

1146
01:15:23,051 --> 01:15:24,211
Hey, hello!

1147
01:15:24,319 --> 01:15:25,877
Good, celery. Parsley, maybe.

1148
01:15:26,355 --> 01:15:28,186
- DESPEREAUX: The Princess is in danger!
- No, no, no.

1149
01:15:28,290 --> 01:15:30,019
