- Oh, no, no, no, of course.

1151
01:15:32,628 --> 01:15:34,027
- It is fantastic!
- Yes.

1152
01:15:34,129 --> 01:15:35,153
<i>Bellissima!</i>

1153
01:15:35,230 --> 01:15:37,061
Brav-ow!

1154
01:15:37,399 --> 01:15:38,457
Oh.

1155
01:15:38,634 --> 01:15:40,727
The Princess is in danger!

1156
01:15:40,836 --> 01:15:41,894
Ooh!

1157
01:15:44,172 --> 01:15:46,572
You are a cute little mouse.

1158
01:15:47,409 --> 01:15:49,036
