1159
01:15:49,144 --> 01:15:50,202
No, I don't want...

1160
01:15:50,312 --> 01:15:52,507
The Princess is in danger!

1161
01:15:52,581 --> 01:15:54,173
And a talking mouse, too.

1162
01:15:54,249 --> 01:15:55,682
Listen, you've gotta help me.

1163
01:15:55,751 --> 01:15:57,343
Perhaps a little cheese?

1164
01:15:57,419 --> 01:15:59,683
No, I don't want any cheese!

1165
01:15:59,755 --> 01:16:02,315
The Princess! She's in danger!

1166
01:16:02,391 --> 01:16:04,052
She's locked in the dungeon!

1167
01:16:04,159 --> 01:16:05,217
(GASPS)

1168
01:16:05,327 --> 01:16:06,351
In the dungeon!

1169
01:16:06,428 --> 01:16:08,760
Oh, don't be silly, my little mouse.

1170
01:16:08,864 --> 01:16:10,422
Everything is fine!

1171
01:16:10,532 --> 01:16:13,660
The Princess is perfectly
safe up in her...

1172
01:16:13,769 --> 01:16:14,827
(GASPS)

1173
01:16:21,777 --> 01:16:24,371
(VILLAGERS CHATTERING EXCITEDLY)

1174
01:16:28,717 --> 01:16:29,741
Oh, my.

1175
01:16:30,052 --> 01:16:31,542
Boldo!

1176
01:16:31,720 --> 01:16:33,244
Look! It's...

1177
01:16:34,623 --> 01:16:35,681
Boldo.

1178
01:16:36,458 --> 01:16:37,720
Where are you?

1179
01:16:38,860 --> 01:16:41,124
Charge!

1180
01:16:42,097 --> 01:16:43,189
Tell me again.

1181
01:16:43,265 --> 01:16:44,289
- Chivalry!
- Mmm.

1182
01:16:44,399 --> 01:16:45,457
- Bravery!
- Mmm-hmm.

1183
01:16:45,567 --> 01:16:46,591
Honor!

1184
01:16:46,702 --> 01:16:50,638
Chivalry! Bravery! Honor!

1185
01:16:50,906 --> 01:16:52,100
I love it!

1186
01:16:52,207 --> 01:16:55,267
Oh, it feels so good to
be out of the kitchen!

1187
01:16:55,711 --> 01:16:57,269
Let's go!

1188
01:16:57,779 --> 01:16:59,713
Into the breach!

1189
01:17:01,083 --> 01:17:02,107
Down there.

1190
01:17:02,217 --> 01:17:03,582
<i>Andiamo!</i>

1191
01:17:05,087 --> 01:17:06,145
Whoa!

1192
01:17:07,956 --> 01:17:09,048
Ha-ha!

1193
01:17:09,958 --> 01:17:10,982
(GASPS)

1194
01:17:15,564 --> 01:17:16,826
