for over two hours.

1228
01:19:24,059 --> 01:19:26,459
My little princess.

1229
01:19:30,432 --> 01:19:31,524
Rain.

1230
01:19:31,600 --> 01:19:32,624
Yes.

1231
01:19:41,076 --> 01:19:42,771
Papa! Papa, look!

1232
01:19:43,078 --> 01:19:44,102
Up there!

1233
01:19:44,446 --> 01:19:45,640
